STATE of North Carolina
v.
Timothy Neal PRINCE No. 151P15-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 7, 2017 Elizabeth N. Strickland, Assistant Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C. Mark Montgomery, Attorney at Law, for Prince, Timothy Neal.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 9th of October 2017 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 7th of December 2017."
